Class AtomicProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.cdk.tools.AtomicProperties

  • public class AtomicProperties
extends Object
    Provides atomic property values for descriptor calculations. This class currently provides values for mass, van der Waals volume, electronegativity and polarizability.
